# Task Management App

[![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-blue.svg)](./LICENSE)
[![Docker](https://img.shields.io/badge/docker-ready-blue.svg)](#docker)
[![Built With Laravel + React](https://img.shields.io/badge/stack-Laravel%20%2B%20React-orange.svg)](#tech-stack)

A full-stack Task Management application with a Laravel API and a React + Vite frontend. Designed for quick local development (Docker-ready) and small-to-medium production deployments.

